videos.description: Kentucky loses control of the ball, and Devontae Shuler knocks down a 3-pointer for Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Shuler knocks in 3 on loose ball) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Shuler knocks in 3 on loose ball

videos.description: After getting his first layup attempt blocked, Nick Richards puts in a bucket and draws a foul.
videos.headline: Richards sinks and-one layup

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey makes a nice pass to Johnny Juzang, who knocks down a deep 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Juzang hits deep 3 for Kentucky) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Juzang hits deep 3 for Kentucky

videos.description: Ole Miss' Blake Hinson dribbles the ball all the way to the baseline and makes a jumper nearly out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Hinson makes tough shot on baseline) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Hinson makes tough shot on baseline

videos.description: Tyrese Maxey deflects the ball and saves it with his own hands, finding Ashton Hagans for the wide-open slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Maxey's steal sets up Hagans' dunk) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Maxey's steal sets up Hagans' dunk

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley tosses an alley-oop lob to Nick Richards, who smashes a dunk in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Quickley, Richards link up for alley-oop slam) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Quickley, Richards link up for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Nick Richards spins to the hoop and dunks one down for Kentucky.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Kentucky's Richards uses nice spin move for dunk) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Kentucky's Richards uses nice spin move for dunk

videos.description: Ole Miss runs the clock down and Devontae Shuler attempts a deep 3-pointer, but he misses it and Kentucky hangs on to win, 67-62.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Ole Miss' Shuler misses key 3 late, Kentucky hangs on) 2020/02/15

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Shuler misses key 3 late, Kentucky hangs on
